law.text:
As used in KRS 367.83801 to 367.83807:
"Customer" means any person who contracts for services with a mold remediation company for the purposes of mold remediation;
"Department" means the Department of Law;
"Mold" means any living or dead fungi or related products or parts, including spores, hyphae, and mycotoxins;
"Mold remediation" means the removal, cleaning, sanitizing, demolition, or other treatment, including preventative activities, of mold or mold-contaminated matter, live or dead, that was not intended to be grown, or purposely grown, at that location; and
"Mold remediation company" means an entity that performs mold remediation for compensation.
